Wow, that&#39;s a very good question. I didn&#39;t even think of that. Very good Ly=
nn! I guess the way to solve that would be to use another recorder to recor=
d the responses. If the recorders are spaced sufficiently the receiving rec=
order should not register something as soft as an EVP from the sending devi=
ce. I guess to some though it would leave enough doubt as to skew any resul=
ts they may get.

Regards,

Frank R.

